article.description: — Jahmir Young scored 15 points and Charlotte defeated UTSA 62-53 on Saturday.
article.headline: Young scores 15, Charlotte topples UTSA 62-53
article.story: CHARLOTTE, N.C. -- — Jahmir Young scored 15 points and Charlotte defeated UTSA 62-53 on Saturday. Robert Braswell added 14 points and Jackson Threadgill scored 11 for the 49ers (9-5, 2-0 C-USA). Christian Tucker led the Roadrunners (7-11, 0-5) with 10 points. Five players scored six. —-
